  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Hancock County IL?",
  "response": "I don't have real-time data, but it is always a good idea to check for updated information and reviews. You can consider these general options:\n\n1. **Wellness Centers in Nearby Cities**: Larger cities near Hancock County may have reputable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers. Quincy, IL and Keokuk, IA are relatively close and likely have more options.\n\n2. **State Resources**: The Illinois Department of Human Services website offers listings of licensed treatment facilities in the state.\n\n3. **Online Directories**: Websites like Rehabs.com, SAMHSA's Treatment Locator, or Psychology Today's therapy directory can help you find treatment facilities based on your location.\n\n4. **Local Healthcare Providers**: Consult with a local healthcare provider in Hancock County for recommendations and referrals to reputable rehab centers that offer inpatient services.\n\n5. **Community Support Services**: Contacting local groups such as Alcoholics Anonymous (AA) or Narcotics Anonymous (NA) can also provide guidance and information on nearby inpatient rehab centers. \n\nAlways ensure to verify the credentials, treatment methods, and reviews of any rehab center you are considering.",
